        {
            "title": "中國｜商務部：美國301調查典型單邊主義行徑　嚴重破壞國際經貿秩序",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"中國｜商務部：美國301調查典型單邊主義行徑 嚴重破壞國際經貿秩序\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國｜商務部：美國301調查典型單邊主義行徑 嚴重破壞國際經貿秩序</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在北京，商務部回應美國貿易代表辦公室宣佈以產能過剩為由對包括中國在內的16個經濟體發起301調查。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發言人說，301調查是典型的單邊主義行徑，嚴重破壞國際經貿秩序。世貿組織專家組早已裁決，根據301調查採取的關稅措施違反世貿組織規則。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">關於美方所謂的產能過剩論，中方已經多次闡明立場。世界經濟早已成為不可分割的一個整體，生產和消費都是全球性，需要在全球視野下進行供需匹配和調節。如果各國生產只能滿足國內市場需求，就不會有跨境貿易。美方不能狹隘地將超過國內需求的生產能力定義為產能過剩，貼上所謂「過剩」的標籤。美方更無權通過301調查，對交易夥伴是否存在產能過剩進行單方面認定，並採取單邊限制措施。中方注意到，美方又以未禁止進口強迫勞動產品為由，對包括中國在內的60個經濟體發起301調查。中方正在進行分析評估。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">發言人說，中方敦促美方糾正錯誤做法，回到通過對話協商解決問題的正確軌道上來。中方將密切關注事態進展，保留採取一切必要措施的權利，堅決捍衛自身正當權益。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%95%86%E5%8B%99%E9%83%A8-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B301%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%85%B8%E5%9E%8B%E5%96%AE%E9%82%8A%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E8%A1%8C%E5%BE%91-%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%B6%93%E8%B2%BF%E7%A7%A9%E5%BA%8F-081738246.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-13 16:31:29",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "FI專欄｜勿做年金「稅魚」！｜Jan Wong",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"FI專欄｜勿做年金「稅魚」！｜Jan Wong\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cv9GWPIJ1s9Tc7osNE210A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/1f112e5b7533bbacd26b3fa05c237cb5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">FI專欄｜勿做年金「稅魚」！｜Jan Wong</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">每年報稅季節一到，成千上萬打工仔又開始頭痕：究竟買唔買扣稅年金？廣告成日話60,000蚊換到$10,200扣稅額，聽落好吸引，但真係咁簡單？唔使心急！如果你想真正玩轉扣稅遊戲，由「稅奴」變「稅王」，只要跟住呢三步走，你就係稅務大師！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第一步：扣稅項目大掃描<br/> 先停一停，唔好急住衝去買年金！想像吓你月入5萬蚊，扣稅項目爆棚：父母免稅額、子女免稅額、醫療開支……全部加埋，分分鐘稅單「清零」！<br/> 但呢個「零稅出關」背後，往往係生活壓力爆燈——家用、供樓、養仔女，稅局都知你慘，先畀你扣番啲錢。<br/> 快啲check吓自己今年有幾多免稅額未用！好多人都漏咗幾萬蚊扣稅機會，結果白白畀稅局食走。呢一步做好，你已經贏咗一半！</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e4920b44-a82b-3a1e-a143-63dc59cba3f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第二步：年金扣稅係唔係萬能？<br/> 廣告話買60,000扣到$10,200？聽落好正！但事實上要睇你稅階高低先至知。<br/> 如果你稅階係17%，呢筆錢確實抵玩；但萬一你稅階只係2%或6%，60,000換返幾千蚊就變「雞肋」——扣唔到幾多，仲要鎖死筆錢最少8-10年，萬一中途有急用就麻煩！<br/> 真係划唔來。年金唔係人人適合，唔好被廣告沖昏頭腦，先計清楚自己實際得益幾多！</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第三步：揀年金先至係老闆！<br/> 有得揀先至係老闆！唔同保險公司年金，回報都可以天差地遠。<br/> 有啲產品回報高達4%、保證回本期短至8年，幾年後就見錢返嚟；但有啲保證回報低過3%、綁足10幾年，買咗等於抱住個「爛橙」，全部做足功課，先至唔後悔！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果你都想知道自己需唔需要買年金或者買咩年金好，點擊下面連結交流一下！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">懶人包領取連結🔗⬇️<br/> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://shorturl.at/AzFaB;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://shorturl.at/AzFaB\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://shorturl.at/AzFaB</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">想了解更多都可以follow我IG :<br/> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.instagram.com/jan_wong1203;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jan_wong1203\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/jan_wong1203</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">15分鐘快速線上計稅：<br/> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"https\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:https://forms.gle/RgbAaLCgSbaYN1Y26;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://forms.gle/RgbAaLCgSbaYN1Y26\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/RgbAaLCgSbaYN1Y26</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"http\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
